{
  "texts": [
    "He was a nonsmoker and drank wine occasionally.",
    "The ocular history was significant for early-stage primary open-angle glaucoma (on latanoprost {Xalatan}), and he had a normal eye examination a month prior.",
    "On examination at the urgent visit, the BCVA was 20/20 OD and light perception OS, with loss of color vision OS and the presence of a left afferent pupillary defect.",
    "Visual fields to confrontation were full OD and completely depressed OS.",
    "The IOP was 11 OU."
  ]
}